initng: The next generation init system
initng:
initng: Initng is a full replacement of the old and in many ways deprecated
initng: sysvinit tool. It is designed with speed in mind, doing as much
initng: as possible asynchronously. In other words: It will boot your
initng: unix-system much faster, and give you more control and statistics
initng: over your system.
initng: 
initng: remember to add init=/sbin/initng in your grub or lilo config to
initng: use initng"
initng:
